&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A remote-yes company, where you can decide every day whether you work from home, at our Stuttgart or Munich office, or at any&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.designoffices.de/&quot;&gt;Design Office&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;in Germany&lt;/li&gt;
