&lt;h1&gt;Your Mission&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Marketing AI Manager, you will be responsible for building and running the AI operating layer in the Marketing Team. Your role, as a senior horizontal enabler, will be to make Product Marketing, Brand Marketing, and Integrated Marketing significantly more productive by turning applicable work into governed AI workflows, reusable agents, and shared systems.&lt;/p&gt;
